w depression.', 'Synergism', 'Brodalumab, Azathioprine, Apremilast, Pirfenidone, Belumosudil, Teprotumumab, Emapalumab, Ravulizumab, Pegcetacoplan, Eculizumab, Sutimlimab', 'Cyclosporine, Antithymocyte immunoglobulin (rabbit), Tocilizumab, Secukinumab, Ravulizumab, Mycophenolic acid, Methotrexate, Tacrolimus, Abatacept, Apremilast, Inebilizumab, More', 'Moderate', NULL, 'DDInter', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/37188/', '[1] Cerner Multum, Inc. "Australian Product Information." O 0[2] Cerner Multum, Inc. "UK Summary of Product Characteristics." O 0[3] "Product Information. Lonsurf (tipiracil-trifluridine)." Taiho Oncology, Inc., Princeton, NJ.', 1767369485);
